{"tid":1550083,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[9月8日美領] 美國國歌唔該唱熟啲 莊重啲","createTime":"2019-09-07T14:17:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-07T21:18:06.000Z","uid":148187,"like":89,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":59,"replies":[{"pid":"067a68aa78eca5e12ba46f0c8f3f6696a5aa5328","tid":1550083,"uid":148187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T14:17:30.000Z","msg":"唔該咁多位手足為聽日唱熟啲老美國歌！即使大家好耐冇莊重咁唱過國歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 請唔好忘記唱國歌應該點樣顯得莊重！<br />\n<br />\n美國國歌創作靈感源自美國人喺第二次獨立戰爭奮勇抵抗英軍進攻，而內容講述國旗經歷戰爭依然屹立，強調美國人嘅自由同埋勇氣。美國人唱國歌係會好投入，甚至會唱到喊。國家經打拚得到自由，佢哋認同國家歷史、自由所以愛國（認同自由嘅價值亦係我哋唱老美國歌嘅原因）。<br />\n<br />\n美國人唱國歌嘅時候都有啲禮儀，希望大家留意吓以表尊重：<br />\n(1) 可以雙手擺後/自然垂低<br />\n(2) 將手放喺心口<br />\n(3) 帶帽嘅話會除帽蓋喺心口<br />\n(4) 只有軍人會做敬禮姿勢<br />\n如果聽日唔識唱/未唱熟就唔好拎住手機唱，將手擺喺心口就夠。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WTed1bo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWTed1bo.jpg&h=72d884f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RGvwNRp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRGvwNRp.jpg&h=3fcc800c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vMeaiX4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvMeaiX4.jpg&h=79e67e4d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後梗係唔少得附上美國國歌：<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/vPKp29Luryc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FvPKp29Luryc&d=2M92vpXgCVs0KpVIJKRQC5S3ibws79Cb3MvuL7akqOg%3D&h=eb97d1e4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/vPKp29Luryc</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/PWMy7Rpk5Bo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FPWMy7Rpk5Bo&d=2M92vpXgCVs0KpVIJKRQC5S3ibws79Cb3MvuL7akqOg%3D&h=52f4e982\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/PWMy7Rpk5Bo</a><br />\n<br />\n小弟啲資料係上網搵，有錯請屌細力啲，多多指教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19971686b0277a67dcfa4a91088365cefab257c1","tid":1550083,"uid":157857,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T14:18:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"839bad0b8ea22d0243dc593ca1518f8c8642c0c9","tid":1550083,"uid":90743,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T14:18:46.000Z","msg":"同意 唔好到時先拎手機睇歌詞啦 依家唱熟左先"},{"pid":"b9ac1f7eeda0106c4bc9c8bf55b99e7fc58f756a","tid":1550083,"uid":40902,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T14:18:53.000Z","msg":"想印國旗的手足注意<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1gZQ3qP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1gZQ3qP.jpg&h=4ea160fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/afwzLEa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FafwzLEa.jpg&h=aae7bc4b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/j3B4oqQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fj3B4oqQ.jpg&h=abb40a49&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n聽日用完唔好即棄！拎番番屋企！"},{"pid":"76d5a5cdde0bf5cc7540424630fbb28c8d875007","tid":1550083,"uid":263197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"839bad0b8ea22d0243dc593ca1518f8c8642c0c9","tid":1550083,"uid":90743,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T14:18:46.000Z","msg":"同意 唔好到時先拎手機睇歌詞啦 依家唱熟左先"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T14:19:03.000Z","msg":"同意"},{"pid":"9c55180a5f5570198112ed4af6a05a34c69e2a41","tid":1550083,"uid":199257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T14:20:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa7f354f04b5290fac96ce7f6090e784b4eb74ab","tid":1550083,"uid":148187,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T14:20:04.000Z","msg":"可能會有外媒訪問大家關於法案同埋國歌，請大家了解清楚個法案，亦都要理解吓國歌啲歌詞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4825b99513ad0fb50a44f7324e7bc62247800ec","tid":1550083,"uid":