s we watched were so gallantly streaming?<br />\n仲喺我哋的堡壘上面飄揚緊？<br />\nAnd the rocket's red glare, the bombs bursting in air,<br />\n火箭嘅紅光同喺天空爆炸的炸彈<br />\nGave proof through the night that our flag was still there.<br />\n都喺度見證我哋嘅國旗仲喺到<br />\nOh, say does that star-spangled banner yet wave<br />\n噢，你有無見到星條旗飄揚緊<br />\nO'er the land of the free and the home of the brave?<br />\n喺自由嘅土地同勇敢嘅家鄉？<br />\n<br />\nfrom wiki"},{"pid":"7899eb26438a749f180c550dd2ddfb69b24bbce2","tid":1550083,"uid":95501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"067a68aa78eca5e12ba46f0c8f3f6696a5aa5328","tid":1550083,"uid":148187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T14:17:30.000Z","msg":"唔該咁多位手足為聽日唱熟啲老美國歌！即使大家好耐冇莊重咁唱過國歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 請唔好忘記唱國歌應該點樣顯得莊重！<br />\n<br />\n美國國歌創作靈感源自美國人喺第二次獨立戰爭奮勇抵抗英軍進攻，而內容講述國旗經歷戰爭依然屹立，強調美國人嘅自由同埋勇氣。美國人唱國歌係會好投入，甚至會唱到喊。國家經打拚得到自由，佢哋認同國家歷史、自由所以愛國（認同自由嘅價值亦係我哋唱老美國歌嘅原因）。<br />\n<br />\n美國人唱國歌嘅時候都有啲禮儀，希望大家留意吓以表尊重：<br />\n(1) 可以雙手擺後/自然垂低<br />\n(2) 將手放喺心口<br />\n(3) 帶帽嘅話會除帽蓋喺心口<br />\n(4) 只有軍人會做敬禮姿勢<br />\n如果聽日唔識唱/未唱熟就唔好拎住手機唱，將手擺喺心口就夠。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WTed1bo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWTed1bo.jpg&h=72d884f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RGvwNRp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRGvwNRp.jpg&h=3fcc800c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vMeaiX4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvMeaiX4.jpg&h=79e67e4d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後梗係唔少得附上美國國歌：<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/vPKp29Luryc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FvPKp29Luryc&d=2M92vpXgCVs0KpVIJKRQC5S3ibws79Cb3MvuL7akqOg%3D&h=eb97d1e4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/vPKp29Luryc</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/PWMy7Rpk5Bo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2F